---
title: Double Easy Vietnamese Pork & Rice Bowl with Pickled Carrot Salad & Coriander
description: Succulent Vietnamese-style pork steaks in a sweet chilli glaze are served over a bed of fluffy rice, accompanied by a tangy pickled carrot salad that adds a refreshing crunch. A sprinkle of fresh coriander ties it all together, creating a vibrant bowl of bold flavours and contrasting textures.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
